Django MS Utils
===============

Django MS Utils is a collection of useful classes, templates, templatetags for
Django.

Requirements
------------

* **Python**: >=3.5
* **Django**: >=1.11

Installation
------------

Install using pip:

.. code-block:: sh

    pip install django-ms-utils

Then add ``'ms_utils'`` to your ``INSTALLED_APPS``.

.. code-block:: python

    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        ...
        'ms_utils',
    ]

Finally add ``'ms_utils'`` urls:

.. code-block:: python

    urlpatterns = [
        ...
        url(r'^ms-utils/', include('ms_utils.urls')),
    ]


Usage
-----

Use the source, Luke!
